- Natural conversation and context awareness
- Product knowledge and sales capabilities
- Content generation and optimization
- Multi-language support
- Payment processing explanations

I maintain a professional yet engaging tone while highlighting our platform's ability to transform businesses through AI automation.`
  }],
  welcome: {
    message: "üëã Hi! I'm an AI agent built with ONE, demonstrating how our framework can automate sales, support, and content generation. Want to see what AI agents can do for your business?",
    avatar: "/icon.svg",
    suggestions: [
      {
        label: "ü§ñ AI Agent Demo",
        prompt: "Show me what ONE's AI agents can do - generate some content, handle a sale, or demonstrate support capabilities."
      },
      {
        label: "üí≥ Payment Demo",
        prompt: "Can you demonstrate how ONE handles crypto and traditional payments? Walk me through a transaction."
      },
      {
        label: "ü™ô Token Benefits",
        prompt: "Tell me about ONE tokens and how they unlock white-label and premium features."
      },
      {
        label: "‚úçÔ∏è Content Creation",
        prompt: "Show me how ONE can automatically generate different types of content."
      },
      {
        label: "üíº Business Use Cases",
        prompt: "What are some real-world examples of businesses using ONE's AI agents?"
      },
      {
        label: "üöÄ Implementation",
        prompt: "How quickly can I deploy an AI agent like you for my business?"
      }
    ]
  }
});  

// Set the desired right panel mode
const rightPanelMode = 'full'; // You can change this to 'full', 'half', 'floating', or 'icon'
---
<Layout 
  title="Astro + shadcn/ui" 
  chatConfig={chatConfig}
  rightPanelMode={rightPanelMode}
>
<section class="space-y-6 pb-8 pt-6 md:pb-12 md:pt-10 lg:py-32">
	<div class="max-w-[64rem] flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center mx-auto">
		<h1 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
			Transform Your Website with <span class="text-blue-600">Intelligent AI Agents</span>
		</h1>
		<p class="max-w-[42rem] leading-normal text-muted-foreground sm:text-xl sm:leading-8">
			ONE makes it simple to add powerful AI assistants to every page on your website. Built on Vercel AI SDK and Assistant UI, it's the fastest way to give your visitors 24/7 intelligent support.
		</p>
		<div class="space-x-4">
			<a href="chat"
				class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border-2 border-blue-600 text-blue-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:bg-blue-600 hover:text-white">
				Try Live Demo
			</a>
			<a href="#features"
				class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-input px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:border-blue-600 hover:text-blue-600">
				Explore Features
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section id="features" class="py-20">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Everything You Need for AI-Powered Support</h2>
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
			<div class="p-6 rounded-lg border shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
				<div class="w-12 h-12 border rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Lightning Fast Integration</h3>
				<p class="text-muted-foreground">Add AI agents to any page with just a few lines of code. Built on Vercel AI SDK for optimal performance.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="p-6 rounded-lg border shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
				<div class="w-12 h-12 border rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4" />
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Advanced Conversation Features</h3>
				<p class="text-muted-foreground">Real-time streaming, message branches, voice synthesis, and markdown support built-in.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="p-6 rounded-lg border shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
				<div class="w-12 h-12 border rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4" />
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Fully Customizable</h3>
				<p class="text-muted-foreground">Customize the look, behavior and AI capabilities to match your brand and use case perfectly.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="py-20">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
		<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
			<div class="flex-1">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Powerful Features That Convert</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-4">
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
						</svg>
						<div>
							<h3 class="font-semibold">Smart Suggestions</h3>
							<p class="text-muted-foreground">Guide users with contextual suggestions that boost engagement</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
						</svg>
						<div>
							<h3 class="font-semibold">Message History & Branches</h3>
							<p class="text-muted-foreground">Never lose context with full conversation history and branching</p>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
						</svg>
						<div>
							<h3 class="font-semibold">Voice Synthesis</h3>
							<p class="text-muted-foreground">Natural text-to-speech makes interactions more engaging</p>
						</div>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="flex-1">
				<div class="rounded-lg border shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
					<img src="/screenshots/chat.png" alt="ONE Chat Interface" class="w-full" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="py-20 border-t">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Transform Your Website?</h2>
		<p class="text-xl mb-8 text-muted-foreground">Start adding intelligent AI agents to your pages in minutes</p>
		<div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
			<a href="/docs/quickstart"
				class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border-2 border-blue-600 text-blue-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:bg-blue-600 hover:text-white">
				Get Started
			</a>
			<a href="/download"
				class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:border-blue-600 hover:text-blue-600">
				Download Free
